\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 3. T. tomentosus} Willd.,{\i  Enum. Pl. Hort. Berol.} 626 (1809). Like {\b 2} but leaves c. 5 × 1·5 mm, entire, tomentose; inflorescence c. 7 mm in diameter, denser and more globose; bracts not similar to the leaves; calyx 3-4 mm, the upper teeth 1-2 mm. •{\i  S. Portugal, S.W. Spain.} Hs Lu.
